p One of the most popular features was a search engine that allowed users to look up any ingredient, alcohol, or product to determine if it was vegan or tested on animals.
p I relied on a few third party services to supply the data but also counted on crowdsourcing to do the rest. Unfortunately, the project proved to be expensive in time and money to maintain. Once I had VeganKit launched, I came to the conclusion that Google-searches were satisfactory for looking up such information, and VeganKit was a better use of my time.
