p The iPhone app was built around the time when the first or second iPhone was the latest and greatest. The process of making an app was much more difficult than it is today.
p The purpose of the iPhone app was very simple. By storing the database locally, within the app, users could check ingredients and products wherever they were. No need to have a signal or wait to download data.
